<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">In the <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Drag &amp; Drop Editor</em>, select your desired block that will display the order information, then add your variables.</p>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">We recommend formatting numbers using <a href="https://help.sendinblue.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000268730?tap_a=30591-fb13f0&amp;tap_s=840216-5153c7" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">floatformat</a>. In the example below, we have added:</p>
<ul sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">{{ params.currency | floatformat: 2 }}</code> - the currency of the order</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">{{ params.subtotal | floatformat: 2 }}</code> - the subtotal of the order</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">{{ params.discount | floatformat: 2 }}</code> - the discount of the order</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">{{ params.total | floatformat: 2 }}</code> - the total of the order</li>
</ul>
