<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="73">Now let's personalize the email template with ordered items. To do so, we're using the <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="73">New Template Language</em> to insert a dynamic list.</p>
