<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="97">In the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="97">variable</strong> field, type <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="97">item</code>.</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="98">Set the limit for the number of items that will be displayed. For example, if there are 5 items, and you set 3 as the limit, only 3 items will be shown in the email.</li>
