<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="122">A customer has to be identified by their email address to trigger the workflow, that is, a customer should be logged in to their account on your nopCommerce store or enter their email address during checkout.</p>
</div>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="124">Navigate to the <a href="https://automation.sendinblue.com/?tap_a=30591-fb13f0&amp;tap_s=840216-5153c7" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="124">Automation</a> tab of your Sendinblue account.</p>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="126">Click <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="126">+ CREATE A NEW WORKFLOW</strong>, then select <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="126">Product Purchase</strong> and follow the steps.</p>
