<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="130">Select <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="130">Custom Event (Track Event)</em>.</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="131">Type <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/send-an-order-confirmation-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="131">order_completed</code>.</li>
